= 0.1.1

== FEATURES

=== batch_create
add batch_create configurations in active_scaffold_config, and a table action "Batch Create New" will appear after "Create New" button, and those columns defined in config.batch_create.batch_columns can be input multi-line or multi-selected.A multiplication combination will be created in batch.

==== install 
merge frontends/ext/_form_attribute.rhtml to your template overrides.

==== config
config.actions.add batch_create
config.batch_create.batch_columns = :spec, :size, :brand
config.batch_create.ignore_columns = :name

==== form override
def brand_batch_form_column(record, input_name)
  select_tag input_name ...
end

